        "title": "Sun Haven (video game)",
        "content": "{{short description|2023 video game}}\n{{use mdy dates|date=November 2024}}\n{{Infobox video game\n| title = Sun Haven\n| image = \n| alt = \n| caption = \n| released = March 11, 2023 (Windows)<br>November 29, 2024 (Switch){{efn|in the United States, Canada, Mexico, Brazil, Argentina, Chile, Colombia, and Peru only}}\n| developer = Pixel Sprout Studios\n| publisher = Pixel Sprout Studios\n| platforms = [[Windows]], [[Nintendo Switch]]\n| genre = [[Cozy game|Cozy]], [[farm sim]], [[role-playing video game|RPG]]\n| modes = [[Singleplayer]], [[multiplayer]]{{efn|Windows only}}\n}}\n'''''Sun Haven''''' is a 2023 [[cozy game|cozy]] [[farm sim]], [[role-playing video game|RPG]] video game developed and published by American indie studio Pixel Sprout Studios. The video game was released in March 11, 2023, and is due to release on the [[Nintendo Switch]] in the [[Americas]] in November 29, 2024. It has similarities to other farm sims, especially ''[[Stardew Valley]]'' and ''[[My Time at Sandrock]]''.\n\n== Gameplay ==\nSun Haven is a farm sim video game where players can farm, fish, mine, combat and romance NPCs, similar to ''Stardew Valley'' and ''My Time at Sandrock''. Players start off with a cutscene with Lynn, and then move on to the train. A blackout then occurs on board the train with all the lights going out. Once the player arrives in the town of Sun Haven, they would then have the option of placing their house anywhere on their farm. Players even have the option to marry Lucia, the leader of Sun Haven.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Oaks |first1=Amanda Kay |title=All Sun Haven Marriage Candidates & Romance Guide |url=https://www.escapistmagazine.com/all-sun-haven-marriage-candidates-romance-guide/#h-lucia |website=The Escapist |date=19 August 2024}}</ref> Unlike many other farm sims, this one doesn't have stamina.<ref>{{cite web |title=Tips and Tricks for Beginners - Sun Haven Guide |url=https://www.ign.com/wikis/sun-haven/Tips_and_Tricks_for_Beginners |website=IGN |language=en |date=20 August 2023}}</ref> In addition to Sun Haven, this game features three other towns that the player will discover.\n\n==Development==\nPixel Sprout Studios is an American indie studio, based in [[Los Angeles]]. As of November 2024, this was the only game they worked on.<ref>[https://www.pixelsproutstudios.com/about About - Pixel Sprout Studios] Retrieved November 19, 2024</ref> It was initially on [[early access]] at June 25, 2021, before fully releasing on March 11, 2023.<ref name=PCGamesN /> It was initially due to be in early access for six months.<ref name=PCGamesN>{{cite web |title=Sun Haven is Stardew Valley, but with D&D |url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/sun-haven/steam |website=PCGamesN |date=25 June 2021}}</ref> The game is due to enter the Nintendo Switch on November 29, 2024 in the United States, Canada, Mexico, Brazil, Argentina, Chile, Colombia and Peru.<ref name=Siliconera>{{cite web |last1=Lada |first1=Jenni |title=Move Into the Sun Haven Switch Version in November |url=https://www.siliconera.com/move-into-the-sun-haven-switch-version-in-november/ |website=Siliconera |date=18 November 2024}}</ref> However, [[cross-platform play]] will initially not be available, alongside multiplayer.<ref name=Siliconera/> There are also further plans to release this game onto other consoles in the forseeable future.<ref name=\"SH subreddit announcement\">[https://www.reddit.com/r/SunHaven/comments/1gswtgu/sun_haven_is_coming_to_the_nintendo_switch/ Sun Haven is coming to the Nintendo Switch! : r/SunHaven] Reddit. retrieved 19 november 2024.</ref>\n\n==Reception==\n<!-- note: https://www.metacritic.com/game/sun-haven/ doesn't have anything yet -->\n''Sun Haven'' has received favorable reviews from critics and has often been compared to ''[[Stardew Valley]]''. An [[early access]] review from ''[[PCGamesN]]'' that \"the world has awoken to the charm of this particular hybrid between RPG games and farming games\".<ref name=PCGamesN/> Another early access review from ''[[RPGFan]]'' stated that the game is a \"mystical world\" which is \"inviting, endearing, and quite original\".<ref name=\"RPGFan\">{{cite web |title=Hands-On with Sun Haven: Preview {{!}} RPGFan |url=https://www.rpgfan.com/2021/08/03/hands-on-with-sun-haven-preview/ |website=www.rpgfan.com |date=3 August 2021}}</ref> Meanwhile, after full release, Anna Koselke on ''[[GamesRadar+]]'' states that this game is pretty much like Stardew Valley, but more magical and fantastic.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Koselke |first1=Anna |title=Sun Haven is Stardew Valley's stunning magical twin sister, and the indie game just got its biggest update yet - adding a sand-sational underwater region, charming new bachelors to marry, and more |url=https://www.gamesradar.com/games/simulation/sun-haven-is-stardew-valleys-stunning-magical-twin-sister-and-the-indie-game-just-got-its-biggest-update-yet-adding-a-sand-sational-underwater-region-charming-new-bachelors-to-marry-and-more/ |website=gamesradar |language=en |date=13 June 2024}}</ref> ''[[WIRED]]'' states that the game is 'cozy' and that \"the storyline is rich\".<ref>{{cite web |last1=Strampe |first1=Louryn |title=The Best Cozy Games for Long, Cold Nights |url=https://www.wired.com/gallery/best-cozy-games/ |website=[[WIRED]] |date=10 November 2023}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n===Notes===\n{{notelist}}\n===Sources===\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[https://www.pixelsproutstudios.com/ Official website]\n[[category:2023 video games]]\n[[category:Windows games]]\n[[category:cozy games]]\n[[category:Nintendo Switch games]]\n[[Category:Cooperative video games]]\n[[Category:Multiplayer and single-player video games]]\n[[Category:Indie games]]\n[[Category:Farm life sim video games]]\n[[Category:Life simulation games]]\n[[Category:Role-playing video games]]\n[[Category:Video games developed in the United States]]"
