        "content": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2023}}\n{{short description|Commune in Auvergne-Rhône-Alpes, France}}\n{{Expand French|topic=geo|date=December 2008|Marchamp}}\n\n{{Infobox French commune\n|name                   = Marchamp\n|commune status         = [[Communes of France|Commune]]\n|image                  = Tourbiere Cerin.jpg\n|caption                = Cerin Lake\n|arrondissement         = Belley\n|canton                 = Lagnieu\n|INSEE                  = 01233\n|postal code            = 01680\n|mayor                  = Jean Marcelli<ref>{{cite web|title=Répertoire national des élus: les maires|url=https://www.data.gouv.fr/fr/datasets/r/2876a346-d50c-4911-934e-19ee07b0e503|website=data.gouv.fr, Plateforme ouverte des données publiques françaises|date=2 December 2020|language=fr|access-date=6 May 2024|archive-date=28 June 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628030259/https://www.data.gouv.fr/fr/datasets/r/2876a346-d50c-4911-934e-19ee07b0e503|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|term                   = 2020&ndash;2026\n|intercommunality       = \n|coordinates            = {{coord|45.7833|5.55|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n|elevation m            = 594\n|elevation min m        = 400\n|elevation max m        = 940\n|area km2               = 13.11\n|population             = {{France metadata Wikidata|population_total}}\n|population date        = {{France metadata Wikidata|population_as_of}}\n|population footnotes   = {{France metadata Wikidata|population_footnotes}}\n}}\n\n'''Marchamp''' ({{IPA|fr|maʁʃɑ̃}}) is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Ain]] [[Departments of France|department]] in eastern [[France]].\n\n==Population==\n{{Historical populations\n|source = INSEE<ref name=pophist>[https://www.insee.fr/fr/statistiques/7633058?geo=COM-01233#ancre-POP_T1 Population en historique depuis 1968] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231210233251/https://www.insee.fr/fr/statistiques/7633058?geo=COM-01233#ancre-POP_T1 |date=10 December 2023 }}, INSEE</ref>\n|percentages = pagr\n|align = none\n|1968 |145\n|1975 |113\n|1982 |106\n|1990 |106\n|1999 |108\n|2009 |113\n|2014 |130\n|2020 |130\n}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Communes of the Ain department]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{commons category}}\n{{Ain communes}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Communes of Ain]]\n[[Category:Ain communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia]]\n\n\n{{Ain-geo-stub}}"
