        "title": "Pterolophia holorufa",
        "content": "{{short description|Species of beetle}}\n\n{{Speciesbox\n| taxon = Pterolophia holorufa\n| authority = Breuning, 1969\n| synonyms = \n}}\n\n'''''Pterolophia holorufa''''' is a species of [[beetle]] in the family [[Cerambycidae]]. It was described by [[Stephan von Breuning (entomologist)|Stephan von Breuning]] in 1969. It is known from [[Borneo]].<ref>[https://www.biolib.cz/en/taxon/id255125/ BioLib.cz - ''Pterolophia holorufa''].  Retrieved on 8 September 2014.</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q14739718}}\n\n[[Category:Pterolophia|holorufa]]\n[[Category:Beetles described in 1969]]\n\n\n{{Pterolophia-stub}}"
