        "content": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2023}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{more citations needed|date=March 2014}}\n{{Notability|1=Music|date=January 2021}}\n}}\n{{Infobox album\n| name       = Vamos Tirando\n| type       = Album\n| artist     = [[Platero y Tú]]\n| cover      = Vamos tirando.jpg\n| alt        =\n| released   = 30 April 1993\n| recorded   = March 1993\n| venue      =\n| studio     =\n| genre      = [[Rock and roll]], [[hard rock]], [[blues rock]]\n| length     = 45:30\n| label      = [[Dro Records|DRO]]\n| producer   = Platero y Tú\n| prev_title = [[Muy Deficiente]]\n| prev_year  = 1992\n| next_title = [[Hay Poco Rock & Roll]]\n| next_year  = 1994\n| misc       = {{Singles\n | name        = Vamos tirando\n | type        = Studio\n | single1     = Mari Madalenas\n | single1date =\n | single2     = Esta noche yo haría\n | single2date =\n | single3     = No me hagas soplar\n | single3date =\n | single4     = Tras la barra\n | single4date =\n}}\n}}\n'''''Vamos Tirando''''' is the fourth studio album by Spanish rock band [[Platero y Tú]]. It was produced by Platero y Tú, recorded in March 1993<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.es/Vamos-Tirando-Platero-Y-Tu/dp/B000059QS4/ref=pd_sim_m_6?ie=UTF8&refRID=14H8A83TB1VDDX9G632K|title=Vamos Tirando|work=amazon.es|access-date=22 March 2014}}</ref> and published by [[Dro Records|DRO]] on 30 April 1993.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/vamos-tirando-mw0001514037|title=Vamos Tirandowork=allmusic.com| website=[[AllMusic]] |access-date=22 March 2014}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| title1          = A un tipo listo\n| writer1         = [[Iñaki Antón]] / [[Fito Cabrales]] / [[Jesús García Castilla|Jesús]]\n| length1         = 5:16\n| title2          = Esta noche yo haría\n| writer2         = [[Iñaki Antón]] / [[Fito Cabrales]]\n| length2         = 3:17\n| title3          = No me hagas soplar\n| writer3         = [[Iñaki Antón]] / [[Fito Cabrales]]\n| length3         = 3:16\n| title4          = Marabao\n| writer4         = [[Iñaki Antón]] / [[Fito Cabrales]]\n| length4         = 3:16\n| title5          = Lo que os merecéis\n| writer5         = [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]] / [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]]\n| length5         = 2:23\n| title6          = R&R Batzokian\n| writer6         = [[Josu Zabala]]\n| length6         = 5:19\n| title7          = Bobo\n| writer7         = [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]] / [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]]\n| length7         = 3:05\n| title8          = Mari Madalenas\n| writer8         = [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]] / [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]]\n| length8         = 3:44\n| title9          = Tras la barra\n| writer9         = [[Iñaki Antón]] / [[Fito Cabrales]]\n| length9         = 3:13\n| title10         = Me dan miedo las noches\n| writer10        = [[Juantxu Olano|Juantxu]] / [[Jesús García Castilla|Jesús]] / [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]] / [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]]\n| length10        = 3:58\n| title11         = Mírame\n| writer11        = [[Juantxu Olano|Juantxu]] / [[Jesús García Castilla|Jesús]] / [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]] / [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]]\n| length11        = 5:16\n| title12         = No estoy loco\n| writer12        = [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki]] / [[Fito Cabrales|Fito]]\n| length12        = 3:33\n}}\n\n== Personnel ==\n* [[Fito Cabrales]]: Vocals and guitar.\n* [[Iñaki Antón|Iñaki \"Uoho\" Antón]]: Guitar.\n* Juantxu Olano: Bass.\n* Jesús García: Drums.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20130615215316/http://plateroytu.com/ Platero y Tú official website (in Spanish)]\n\n{{Platero y Tú}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:1993 albums]]\n[[Category:Platero y Tú albums]]\n[[Category:1990s Spanish-language albums]]\n\n\n{{1990s-hard-rock-album-stub}}"
