        "title": "Norfolk Island at the 2010 Commonwealth Games",
        "content": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=May 2018}}\n{{infobox country at games\n| CGA = NFI\n| CGAname = [[Norfolk Island Amateur Sports and Commonwealth Games Association]]\n| games = Commonwealth Games\n| year = 2010\n| flagcaption = \n| oldcode = \n| website = {{url|1=oceaniasport.com/index.php?id=82|2=oceaniasport.com/ }}\n| location = [[Delhi]], [[India]]\n| competitors = 22\n| sports = \n| flagbearer = Opening: [[Duncan Gray (squash player)|Duncan Gray]]<ref>The Norfolk Islander Vol 45, No. 38</ref><br />Closing: [[Michael Graham (archer)|Michael Graham]]<ref>The Norfolk Islander Vol 45. No. 39</ref>\n| rank = \n| gold = 0\n| silver = 0\n| bronze = 0\n| officials = \n| app_begin_year = 1986\n| app_end_year = \n| seealso = \n}}\n\n'''[[Norfolk Island]]''' competed in the [[2010 Commonwealth Games]] held in [[Delhi]], India, from 3 to 14 October 2010.<ref>[http://www.commonwealthgame2010.com/delhi/participating-countries.html Official list of participating nation] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101020092950/http://commonwealthgame2010.com/delhi/participating-countries.html |date=2010-10-20 }}</ref>\n\n==Team Norfolk Island at the 2010 Commonwealth Games==\n<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://results.cwgdelhi2010.org/en/Root.mvc/CountryInfo/NFK|title = XIX Commonwealth Games 2010 Delhi &#124;}}</ref>\n\n== Archery==\n{{main|Archery at the 2010 Commonwealth Games}}\nTeam Norfolk Island consists of 5 archers.\n\n[[Rosa Ford]], [[Bob Kemp]], [[Michael Graham (archer)|Michael Graham]], [[Jonno Snell]], [[Jo Snell]]\n\nThey competed in the\n* Men's Compound Individual\n* Men's Compound Team\n* Women's Compound Individual\n\n== Lawn Bowls==\n{{main|Lawn bowls at the 2010 Commonwealth Games}}\nTeam Norfolk Island consists of 9 lawn bowls players.\n\n[[Carmen Anderson]], [[Kitha Bailey]], [[John Christian (bowls)|John Christian]], [[Petal Hore]], [[Margaret O'Brien (bowls)|Margaret O'Brien]], [[Anne Pledger]], [[Esther Sanchez]], [[Timothy Sheridan]], [[Barry Wilson (bowls)|Barry Wilson]]\n\nThey competed in the\n* Men's Triples\n* Women's Singles\n* Women's Pairs\n* Women's Triples\n\n== Shooting==\n{{main|Shooting at the 2010 Commonwealth Games}}\nTeam Norfolk Island consists of 4 shooters.\n\nGraham Cock, [[Graham Lock (sport shooter)|Graham Lock]], [[Denise Reeves]], [[Stephen Ryan (sport shooter)|Stephen Ryan]]\n\nThey competed in the\n* Men's Singles 10m Air Pistol\n* Men's Pairs 10m Air Pistol\n* Men's Singles 25m Standard Pistol\n* Men's Pairs 25m Standard Pistol\n* Men's Singles 25m Centrefire Pistol\n* Men's Pairs 25m Centrefire Pistol\n* Women's Singles 10m Air Pistol\n* Women's Singles 25m Pisol\n\n== Squash==\n{{main|Squash at the 2010 Commonwealth Games}}\nTeam Norfolk Island consists of 4 squash players\n\n[[Peter Christian-Bailey]], [[Gye Duncan]], [[Duncan Gray (squash player)|Duncan Gray]], [[Mal Rundell]]\n\nThey competed in the\n* Men's Doubles\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{country at games navbox|Norfolk Island|Commonwealth Games|1986}}\n{{Commonwealth Games Associations at the 2010 Commonwealth Games}}\n\n[[Category:Norfolk Island at the Commonwealth Games]]\n[[Category:Nations at the 2010 Commonwealth Games]]\n[[Category:2010 in Norfolk Island]]\n[[Category:2010 in Australian sport]]\n\n\n{{NorfolkIsland-stub}}"
